        " عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"إِذَا أَرَادَ أَحَدُكُمُ اَلْحَاجَةَ فَلْيُبَكِّرْ إِلَيْهَا وَ لْيُسْرِعِ اَلْمَشْيَ إِلَيْهَا\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3575 - Imam (as) said:\n\"If any of you intends to fulfill a need, let him seek it early in the morning and hasten in walking towards it.\""
